<li id="cite_note-25"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-25">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite class="citation web cs1"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.badarchaeology.com/extraterrestrials/the-sirius-mystery/">"Did the Dogon of Mali know about Sirius B?"</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=Did+the+Dogon+of+Mali+know+about+Sirius+B%3F&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.badarchaeology.com%2Fextraterrestrials%2Fthe-sirius-mystery%2F&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ADogon+people" class="Z3988"></span></span>
</li>
<li id="cite_note-26"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-26">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><a href="#CITEREFGriauleDieterlen1986">Griaule &amp; Dieterlen (1986)</a>, pp.&#160;33–34</span>
</li>
