<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="Art_2">Art</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Dogon_people&amp;action=edit&amp;section=19" title="Edit section: Art"><span>edit</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>
<link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1054258005"><div class="refbegin" style="">
<ul><li><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFEzra,_Kate1988" class="citation book cs1">Ezra, Kate (1988). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://cdm16028.contentdm.oclc.org/cdm/compoundobject/collection/p15324coll10/id/35597"><i>Art of the Dogon: selections from the Lester Wunderman collection</i></a>. New York: The Metropolitan Museum of Art. <a href="/wiki/ISBN_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="ISBN (identifier)">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/978-0-87099-507-1" title="Special:BookSources/978-0-87099-507-1"><bdi>978-0-87099-507-1</bdi></a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Art+of+the+Dogon%3A+selections+from+the+Lester+Wunderman+collection&amp;rft.place=New+York&amp;rft.pub=The+Metropolitan+Museum+of+Art&amp;rft.date=1988&amp;rft.isbn=978-0-87099-507-1&amp;rft.au=Ezra%2C+Kate&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fcdm16028.contentdm.oclc.org%2Fcdm%2Fcompoundobject%2Fcollection%2Fp15324coll10%2Fid%2F35597&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ADogon+people" class="Z3988"></span></li>
<li><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFLaude,_Jean1973" class="citation book cs1">Laude, Jean (1973). <span class="id-lock-registration" title="Free registration required"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://archive.org/details/africanartofdogo00laud"><i>African Art of the Dogon: The Myths of the Cliff Dwellers</i></a></span>. New York: The Viking Press. <a href="/wiki/ISBN_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="ISBN (identifier)">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/978-0-670-10928-9" title="Special:BookSources/978-0-670-10928-9"><bdi>978-0-670-10928-9</bdi></a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=African+Art+of+the+Dogon%3A+The+Myths+of+the+Cliff+Dwellers&amp;rft.place=New+York&amp;rft.pub=The+Viking+Press&amp;rft.date=1973&amp;rft.isbn=978-0-670-10928-9&amp;rft.au=Laude%2C+Jean&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Farchive.org%2Fdetails%2Fafricanartofdogo00laud&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ADogon+people" class="Z3988"></span></li>
